    <item>
      <title>三分之二的英国富裕工党选民对他们的决定感到后悔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/two-thirds-of-wealthy-uk-labour-voters-regret-their-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新调查显示，英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 失去了富裕选民的支持，正是这些选民帮助他领导的工党在去年的英国大选中赢得了历史性多数席位，这一结果凸显了上台七个月的英国政府日益减弱的支持率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/two-thirds-of-wealthy-uk-labour-voters-regret-their-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国要求反垄断监管机构允许在推动经济增长过程中承担更多风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/uk-tells-antitrust-watchdog-to-allow-more-risk-in-growth-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府表示，英国反垄断监管机构在继续向该国监管机构施加压力以刺激经济增长的同时，应该“减少规避风险”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/uk-tells-antitrust-watchdog-to-allow-more-risk-in-growth-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国法官允许特朗普的联邦工作人员买断提议继续进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/us-judge-allows-trump-s-federal-worker-buyout-offer-to-go-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿的一名美国法官周三表示，唐纳德·特朗普针对联邦雇员的买断提议可以继续进行，因为挑战该计划的工会在本案中没有诉讼资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/us-judge-allows-trump-s-federal-worker-buyout-offer-to-go-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 23:39:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加巴德称对美国情报部门的信任度处于“历史最低点”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/tulsi-gabbard-says-trust-in-us-intelligence-community-is-at-all-time-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在参议院批准塔尔西·加巴德出任新任国家情报总监数小时后，她表示，对美国情报界的信任度“处于历史最低点”，并承诺结束她所谓的“武器化和政治化”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/tulsi-gabbard-says-trust-in-us-intelligence-community-is-at-all-time-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 23:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比里亚暂停 400 名未申报财产的高级官员职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/liberia-suspends-400-top-officials-for-non-declaration-of-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比里亚总统约瑟夫·博阿凯已暂停其政府中 400 多名高级官员的职务，原因是他们未能向反腐败机构申报资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/liberia-suspends-400-top-officials-for-non-declaration-of-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 23:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克和 DOGE 的权力不断扩大，但员工和职权范围仍不明确</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/elon-musk-and-doge-powers-expand-while-staff-and-remit-stay-shrouded</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克和他的政府效率部已经侵入了严密保护的美国政府网络，迫使数万名联邦工作人员离职，并让人们普遍感觉到，曾经使官僚机构正常运转的规则正在被撕毁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/elon-musk-and-doge-powers-expand-while-staff-and-remit-stay-shrouded</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 22:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邦迪称美国司法部已就移民案件起诉纽约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/bondi-says-us-doj-has-sued-new-york-over-immigration-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部长帕姆·邦迪周三表示，司法部已就纽约州的移民政策起诉该州及其多名官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/bondi-says-us-doj-has-sued-new-york-over-immigration-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 22:39:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和普京同意就乌克兰问题举行会谈，美国政策出现逆转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-putin-agree-to-negotiate-over-ukraine-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的电话交谈中同意开始就结束乌克兰战争进行谈判，此举一举推翻了美国三年来的政策，也让欧洲盟友措手不及，他们担心美国更为和解的立场相当于向俄罗斯领导人屈服。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-putin-agree-to-negotiate-over-ukraine-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 17:00:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大 13 位州长抵达华盛​​顿，在贸易上打中国牌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/canada-s-13-premiers-descend-on-washington-to-play-the-china-card-on-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大各省和地区领导人周三向华盛顿提出反对关税的诉求，试图传达一个信息：他们可以帮助新政府促进经济增长并与中国竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/canada-s-13-premiers-descend-on-washington-to-play-the-china-card-on-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 13:06:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普可以将墨西哥湾更名为美国湾吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-07/trump-says-he-will-change-the-name-of-the-gulf-of-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（美联社）——四个多世纪以来，从佛罗里达州到德克萨斯州再到墨西哥的这片水域一直被称为墨西哥湾。但几周后，唐纳德·特朗普总统和白宫官员试图改写地图，将其称为美国湾——并坚持要求其他人也这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-07/trump-says-he-will-change-the-name-of-the-gulf-of-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 19:36:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
